  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy-to-learn, but hard to master</strong> motocross game. Perform stunts, gain levels, upgrade your bike and spend resources on customization items of your choosing. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMBO STUNTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/ea7685a7314344856762f39eca1ffe0a.poster.avif?t=1748442670\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/ea7685a7314344856762f39eca1ffe0a.webm?t=1748442670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/ea7685a7314344856762f39eca1ffe0a.mp4?t=1748442670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>  </strong><br><strong>Complete levels </strong>and unlock new bikes. Choose from 10+ unique bikes, each with a different playstyle!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE THE WORLD</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/87ded7864f6aec5fffea35b3473cb7f3.poster.avif?t=1748442670\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/87ded7864f6aec5fffea35b3473cb7f3.webm?t=1748442670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/87ded7864f6aec5fffea35b3473cb7f3.mp4?t=1748442670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From sunny beaches to bustling city streets and frozen lakes</strong>, race through various environments and uncover their secrets. Every level contains hidden collectibles to find.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FLAUNT YOUR GEAR </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/830a5b42b89c1181dac9eff3aee5f4f5.poster.avif?t=1748442670\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/830a5b42b89c1181dac9eff3aee5f4f5.webm?t=1748442670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212130/extras/830a5b42b89c1181dac9eff3aee5f4f5.mp4?t=1748442670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>Spend your hard-earned coin to customize</strong> your character and your bike. Choose from 100+ different items and bike paintjobs to build your own look.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TL;DR</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >400+ Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ Environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main tracks and harder bonus tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ Bikes with customizations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ Character customization items</p></li></ul>",
